72
00:03:25.622 --> 00:03:29.750
I just found out I'm going to be
in Christopher Nolan's new movie.

73
00:03:29.751 --> 00:03:32.252
<i>Charlemagne</i>. with Austin Butler.

74
00:03:32.253 --> 00:03:33.503
Wow. that's huge.

75
00:03:33.504 --> 00:03:38.425
I know. but the movie films in Bulgaria.
and I'll be gone for five months.

76
00:03:38.426 --> 00:03:39.635
Oh. wow.

77
00:03:39.636 --> 00:03:42.179
Well. I'll just come visit you
after the season.

78
00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:43.972
Actually. I used to play in Sofia

79
