in different directions right now.

85
00:04:05.995 --> 00:04:08.872
Is this because
I didn't know who Toni Morrison was?

86
00:04:08.873 --> 00:04:09.957
Toni's a man's name.

87
00:04:09.958 --> 00:04:12.751
No. it's not that.
but you should read more.

88
00:04:12.752 --> 00:04:14.586
I leave in a couple of days.

89
00:04:14.587 --> 00:04:16.713
and you should be focused on
the playoffs anyway.

90
00:04:16.714 --> 00:04:18.675
Wow. I lost my appetite.

91
00:04:19.259 --> 00:04:22.219
Excuse me. Can I have
my Lil' Shogun chicken tenders to go?

92
00:04:22.220 --> 00:04:23.096
Thank you.

93
00:04:26.307 --> 00:04:31.270
With over 185 newly constructed
bus and train routes. the LA Olympics…

94
00:04:31.271 --> 00:04:32.689
Excuse me. Stephen?

95
00:04:33.606 --> 00:04:34.648
Stephen.

96
00:04:34.649 --> 00:04:36.066
Hi. It's Isla. From work.

97
00:04:36.067 --> 00:04:39.027
