a fucking job next season. understand?

149
00:06:55.081 --> 00:06:56.457
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

150
00:06:57.125 --> 00:06:59.042
Okay. Bring it in.

151
00:06:59.043 --> 00:06:59.919
Come on!

152
00:07:01.796 --> 00:07:03.256
