228
00:10:30.338 --> 00:10:31.546
- Where's the vape?
- What?

229
00:10:31.547 --> 00:10:33.256
Isla? Oh my God. What are you doing?

230
00:10:33.257 --> 00:10:35.675
No. what are you doing? Oh… Oh my God!

231
00:10:35.676 --> 00:10:36.676
- Got it.
- Oh my…

232
00:10:36.677 --> 00:10:38.763
